"{\"uid\": \"rte.ie-sport-paris-2024-2024-0731-1462858-paris-2024-wiffen-hardly-slept-after-olympic-gold-win\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Olympic gold medallist Daniel Wiffen said he hardly slept after his 800m freestyle triumph.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 93, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Olympic gold medallist Daniel Wiffen\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 36}, {\"ngram\": \"his 800m freestyle triumph\", \"from\": 64, \"to\": 90}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 23-year-old Armagh manstormed the final stretchin the La Defense Arena to clinch gold in an Olympic record time last night.\", \"from\": 95, \"to\": 222, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 111, \"end\": 117, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Armagh_GAA\", \"score\": 0.830506447198381, \"rank\": 0.20372804023384827, \"text\": \"Armagh\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Armagh_GAA\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Armagh_GAA\"}, {\"begin\": 153, \"end\": 163, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/La_D\\u00e9fense\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"La Defense\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/La_D\\u00e9fense\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/La_D\\u00e9fense\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the final stretchin\", \"from\": 129, \"to\": 148}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 180, \"to\": 184}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic record time\", \"from\": 188, \"to\": 210}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After receiving his medal on the podium, Wiffen said he went straight into anti-doping and then the swim-down before treating himself to some pizza.\", \"from\": 224, \"to\": 372, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his medal\", \"from\": 240, \"to\": 249}, {\"ngram\": \"the podium\", \"from\": 253, \"to\": 263}, {\"ngram\": \"Wiffen\", \"from\": 265, \"to\": 271}, {\"ngram\": \"some pizza\", \"from\": 361, \"to\": 371}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We left the pool at 12.30am, got back into the dining hall, had a couple slices of pizza, then tried to go to bed - did not happen,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 374, \"to\": 516, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the pool\", \"from\": 383, \"to\": 391}, {\"ngram\": \"the dining hall\", \"from\": 418, \"to\": 433}, {\"ngram\": \"a couple slices\", \"from\": 439, \"to\": 454}, {\"ngram\": \"pizza\", \"from\": 458, \"to\": 463}, {\"ngram\": \"bed\", \"from\": 485, \"to\": 488}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Got to bed at about 3.30am and woke up at 7.30 this morning.\", \"from\": 518, \"to\": 579, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I did not get too much sleep but that's not surprising.\", \"from\": 580, \"to\": 635, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"too much sleep\", \"from\": 594, \"to\": 608}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I watched it (the race) before I went to sleep because I knew I would not sleep so I watched it and I am very happy, it was paced to perfection, that's all we can ask for.\", \"from\": 637, \"to\": 809, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the race\", \"from\": 652, \"to\": 660}, {\"ngram\": \"sleep\", \"from\": 679, \"to\": 684}, {\"ngram\": \"perfection\", \"from\": 771, \"to\": 781}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Words can not describe how you feel when you wake up and next to your pillow is an Olympic gold medal.\\\"\", \"from\": 811, \"to\": 915, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Words\", \"from\": 812, \"to\": 817}, {\"ngram\": \"your pillow\", \"from\": 877, \"to\": 888}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic gold medal\", \"from\": 892, \"to\": 913}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gold medal winner Daniel Wiffen speaks to RT\\u00c9 Sport the day after winning gold in the 800m freestyle#RTESport#Paris2024\\ud83d\\udcfa Watchhttps://t.co/b2OI4OoWVJ\\ud83d\\udcf1Updateshttps://t.co/01ShZjM17Cpic.twitter.com/oPd5qDaC0d Wiffen's family - including his twin brother Nathan - were poolside to witness his stunning victory.\", \"from\": 917, \"to\": 1225, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1172, \"end\": 1178, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nathan_Petrelli\", \"score\": 0.9999999999556621, \"rank\": 4.43317330853688e-11, \"text\": \"Nathan\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nathan_Petrelli\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nathan_Petrelli\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Gold medal winner Daniel Wiffen\", \"from\": 917, \"to\": 948}, {\"ngram\": \"RT\\u00c9 Sport\", \"from\": 959, \"to\": 968}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 991, \"to\": 995}, {\"ngram\": \"the 800m\", \"from\": 999, \"to\": 1007}, {\"ngram\": \"his twin brother\", \"from\": 1152, \"to\": 1168}, {\"ngram\": \"his stunning victory\", \"from\": 1203, \"to\": 1223}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He said: \\\"It was amazing to see my twin brother in the crowd, you can not ask for more than that, then my whole family being there.\", \"from\": 1227, \"to\": 1358, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my twin brother\", \"from\": 1259, \"to\": 1274}, {\"ngram\": \"the crowd\", \"from\": 1278, \"to\": 1287}, {\"ngram\": \"my whole family\", \"from\": 1330, \"to\": 1345}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Words just can not describe, seeing my mum crying and that setting me off.\", \"from\": 1360, \"to\": 1435, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Words\", \"from\": 1361, \"to\": 1366}, {\"ngram\": \"my mum\", \"from\": 1397, \"to\": 1403}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And the national anthem, tears going down my face.\", \"from\": 1436, \"to\": 1486, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"And the national anthem\", \"from\": 1436, \"to\": 1459}, {\"ngram\": \"tears\", \"from\": 1461, \"to\": 1466}, {\"ngram\": \"my face\", \"from\": 1478, \"to\": 1485}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have kind of forgotten it because it's gone so quick, but it's so cool.\", \"from\": 1487, \"to\": 1560, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My parents have been driving me to 4.30am practice, it's been a relentless journey.\", \"from\": 1562, \"to\": 1646, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My parents\", \"from\": 1563, \"to\": 1573}, {\"ngram\": \"4.30am practice\", \"from\": 1598, \"to\": 1613}, {\"ngram\": \"a relentless journey\", \"from\": 1625, \"to\": 1645}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have been doing this since I was at least 12-years-old and they kept doing it for me and they are the reason I am here today.\", \"from\": 1647, \"to\": 1774, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the reason\", \"from\": 1747, \"to\": 1757}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They are a massive part, and that's why I say it's never an individual sport, swimming, I have got this whole support network behind me.\\\"\", \"from\": 1776, \"to\": 1914, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a massive part\", \"from\": 1786, \"to\": 1800}, {\"ngram\": \"an individual sport\", \"from\": 1834, \"to\": 1853}, {\"ngram\": \"swimming\", \"from\": 1855, \"to\": 1863}, {\"ngram\": \"this whole support network\", \"from\": 1876, \"to\": 1902}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read more:Meet Daniel Wiffen - Ireland's gold medal winning swimmer Wiffen will now be eyeing more success in the 1500m freestyle, with the heats due to start on Saturday morning.\", \"from\": 1916, \"to\": 2096, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1949, \"end\": 1956, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999999944468527, \"rank\": 5.553087745629561e-09, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"swimmer\", \"from\": 1976, \"to\": 1983}, {\"ngram\": \"more success\", \"from\": 2010, \"to\": 2022}, {\"ngram\": \"the 1500m freestyle\", \"from\": 2026, \"to\": 2045}, {\"ngram\": \"the heats\", \"from\": 2052, \"to\": 2061}, {\"ngram\": \"Saturday morning\", \"from\": 2078, \"to\": 2094}]}, {\"sentence\": \"